OL,3,CGirl, 11, critically injured after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by bin lorry
OL,6,FAn 11-year-old girl has been
OL,7,Fcritically injured after being hit by
OL,8,Fa bin lorry in the Scottish Borders.
OL,10,FThe crash between the girl and lorry
OL,11,Fhappened at around 08.05am on
OL,12,FWednesday 31 January near East Gordon
OL,13,Fon the A6105, close to a junction with
OL,14,Fan unclassified local road.
OL,16,FThe girl, who was a pedestrian, was
OL,17,Ftaken by air ambulance to the Royal
OL,18,FHospital for Children in Edinburgh.
OL,19,FHer condition has been described as
OL,20,Fcritical.
