OL,6,FThe occupants of the bin lorry were
OL,7,Funinjured.
OL,9,FPolice Scotland are now appealing for
OL,10,Fwitnesses to come forward.
OL,12,FInspector Ross Drummond said: "Our
OL,13,Fenquiries into this collision are
OL,14,Fongoing and we are keen to speak to
OL,15,Fthe drivers of other vehicles which
OL,16,Fwere traveling on the A6105 at the
OL,17,Ftime.
